Hello, Happy Holidays.

The Santa's Gold collection is a collection of PHP scripts that builds different pieces of web apps. You can turn them into virtually anything! There's a lesson in every one!

Abstract Character Selection is just another piece of the puzzle in the Santa's Gold Collection. Enjoy this basic script that teaches abstract classes and creates a cool character selection page.

